:"Nov\u00E9 a popul\u00E1rn\u00ED","ContactInfo.Address":"Adresa","ContactInfo.Email":"E-mail","ContactInfo.Name":"N\u00E1zev","Collections.CollectionPosition":"Kolekce {0} z(e) {1}","Footer.ColumnHeaderWhatsNew":"Co je nov\u00E9ho","Footer.ColumnWhatsNewLinkMoreContent":"Dal\u0161\u00ED obsah v Microsoft Storu","Footer.ColumnWhatsNewLinkApps":"Aplikace","Footer.ColumnWhatsNewLinkGames":"Hry","Footer.ColumnWhatsNewLinkThemes":"Motivy","Footer.ColumnWhatsNewLinkWinExpBlog":"Blog o prost\u0159ed\u00ED Windows","Footer.ColumnHeaderMSStore":"Microsoft Store","Footer.ColumnMSStoreLinkAccountProfile":"\u00DA\u010Det Microsoft","Footer.ColumnMSStoreLinkSupport":"Podpora Microsoft Store","Footer.ColumnMSStoreLinkAccountReturns":"Vratky","Footer.ColumnMSStoreLinkFlexPay":"Flexibiln\u00ED platby","Footer.ColumnMSStoreLinkAccountStorePolicy":"Z\u00E1sady a pravidla chov\u00E1n\u00ED","Footer.ColumnMSStoreLinkGetStoreApp":"Z\u00EDskat aplikaci Microsoft Store","Footer.ColumnHeaderForDevelopers":"Pro v\u00FDvoj\u00E1\u0159e","Footer.ColumnForDevsLinkPublishApp":"Publikujte svou aplikaci","Footer.ColumnForDevsLinkAdvWithUs":"Inzerujte u n\u00E1s","Footer.ColumnForDevsLinkGenBadge":"Vytvo\u0159te si vlastn\u00ED odzn\u00E1\u010Dek aplikace","Footer.ColumnHeaderWindows":"Windows","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkCareers":"Kari\u00E9ra","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkAbout":"O spole\u010Dnosti Microsoft","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkNews":"Novinky spole\u010Dnosti","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkInvest":"Investo\u0159i","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkDI":"Rozmanitost a inkluze","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkAccess":"Usnadn\u011Bn\u00ED","Footer.ColumnWindowsLinkSustain":"Udr\u017Eitelnost","Footer.LegalNoticeLink":"Pr\u00E1vn\u00ED ozn\u00E1men\u00ED a informace pro spot\u0159ebitele","Footer.PrivacyChoicesLink":"Va\u0161e volby ochrany osobn\u00EDch \u00FAdaj\u016F","Footer.PrivacyChoicesIcon":"Ikona, kter\u00E1 p\u0159edstavuje mo\u017Enosti volby ochrany osobn\u00EDch \u00FAdaj\u016F","Footer.ManageCookies":"Sprav