0FD obsah na jednom m\u00EDst\u011B.","Apps.Page.Title":"Aplikace na Microsoft Store \u2013 St\u00E1hn\u011Bte si aplikace pro nejvy\u0161\u0161\u00ED produktivitu, kreativitu a z\u00E1bavu pro v\u00E1\u0161 osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010D s Windows","Apps.Page.Description":"Najd\u011Bte si ty nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace pro pr\u00E1ci, kreativitu a z\u00E1bavu. St\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejl\u00E9pe hodnocen\u00E9 n\u00E1stroje a hry pro za\u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED s Windows na Microsoft Store.","Games.Page.Title":"Hry v Microsoft Storu \u2013 objevte a hrajte obl\u00EDben\u00E9 hry pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De s Windows","Games.Page.Description":"Prozkoumejte jedine\u010Dnou kolekci her pro Xbox a osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010D. Hrajte, nakupujte a u\u017Eijte si nov\u00E9 verze a prodejn\u00ED akce na Microsoft Store.","Tencent.Page.Title":"Centrum MyApp \u2013 stahujte mobiln\u00ED aplikace a hry ve Windows","Tencent.Page.Description":"Prozkoumejte centrum Tencent MyApp v Microsoft Store \u2013 m\u00EDsto pro nejnov\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED mobiln\u00ED aplikace a hry ve Windows. Stahujte nyn\u00ED snadno!","Themes.Page.Title":"Motivy \u2013 P\u0159izp\u016Fsoben\u00ED prost\u0159ed\u00ED Windows","Themes.Page.Description":"Objevujte a stahujte motivy, tapety a mo\u017Enosti p\u0159izp\u016Fsoben\u00ED, kter\u00E9 v\u00E1m umo\u017En\u00ED upravit prost\u0159ed\u00ED plochy Windows v Microsoft Store.","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Title":"P\u0159izp\u016Fsobte si sv\u016Fj po\u010D\u00EDta\u010D","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Subtitle":"P\u0159izp\u016Fsobte si sv\u00E9 za\u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED podle sebe","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Description":"P\u0159izp\u016Fsobte si Windows pomoc\u00ED vybran\u00FDch bal\u00ED\u010Dk\u016F motiv\u016F \u2013 nov\u00FDch tapet a barev motiv\u016F","RankDisclosureIcon.Message":"Dal\u0161\u00ED informace o krit\u00E9ri\u00EDch hodnocen\u00ED najdete tady: {0}.","RankDisclosureIcon.AutomationName":"Prohl\u00E1\u0161en\