\u010Dnosti, kter\u00E1 nen\u00ED Microsoft, co\u017E m\u016F\u017Ee m\u00EDt vliv na Nastaven\u00ED rodi\u010Dovsk\u00E9 kontroly pro n\u00E1kupy.","ParentalControl.InfoLearnMore":"Dal\u0161\u00ED informace o n\u00E1kupech v aplikaci a ovl\u00E1dac\u00EDch prvc\u00EDch zabezpe\u010Den\u00ED rodiny","ReinstallBanner.Title":"Z\u00EDskejte aplikaci Microsoft Store","ReinstallBanner.Description":"St\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nebo znovu nainstalujte ofici\u00E1ln\u00ED aplikaci Microsoft Store, kde m\u016F\u017Eete objevovat nov\u00E9 a aktualizovat obl\u00EDben\u00E9 aplikace.","ReinstallBanner.DownloadButton":"St\u00E1hnout","ReinstallBanner.StoreLogoAlt":"Logo Microsoft Store","ReinstallBanner.IconAriaLabel":"P\u0159ej\u00EDt na podrobnosti o aplikaci v Microsoft Store","ReinstallBanner.CloseAriaLabel":"Zav\u0159\u00EDt banner pro p\u0159einstalaci","ReinstallBanner.NonWindows.Title":"Hled\u00E1te aplikaci Microsoft Store?","ReinstallBanner.NonWindows.Description":"Ofici\u00E1ln\u00ED aplikace Microsoft Store kde m\u016F\u017Eete objevovat nov\u00E9 a aktualizovat obl\u00EDben\u00E9 aplikace ve Windows.","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.VerifiedSecureTitle":"Ov\u011B\u0159eno a zabezpe\u010Deno","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.VerifiedSecureDescription":"Aplikace a hry ov\u011B\u0159en\u00E9 Microsoftem pro v\u00E1\u0161 klid","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.EffortlessExperienceTitle":"Hladce funguj\u00EDc\u00ED prost\u0159ed\u00ED","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.EffortlessExperienceDescription":"Instalace jedn\u00EDm kliknut\u00EDm s automatick\u00FDmi aktualizacemi a cloudovou synchronizac\u00ED","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.UniversalAccessTitle":"Univerz\u00E1ln\u00ED p\u0159\u00EDstup","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.UniversalAccessDescription":"Hladk\u00FD p\u0159\u00EDstup k obsahu na v\u0161ech za\u0159\u00EDzen\u00EDch s Windows","MsStoreDetails.DescriptionSection.ExploreButton":"Prozkoumat Microsoft Store","AppPackBanner.Title":"P\u0159edstavujeme instalaci v\u00EDce aplikac\u00ED","AppPackBanner.Description":"Vybrat a nainstalovat n\u011Bkolik aplikac\u00ED najednou","AppPackBanner.AriaLabel":"P\u0159ej\u00EDt na str\u00E1nku bal\u00ED\u010Dku aplikac\u00ED","AppPack.Page.Title":"P\u0159edstavujeme instalaci v\u00EDce aplikac\u00ED ve Windows","AppPack.Page.Description":"Z Microsoft Storu m\u016F\u017Eete vybrat a nainstalovat v\u00EDce aplikac\u00ED pro produktivitu, kreativitu, soci\u00E1ln\u00ED s\u00EDt\u011B a z\u00E1bavu najednou. Zjednodu\u0161te instalaci aplikac\u00ED pomoc\u00ED hromadn\u00E9 instalace.","AppPack.Page.Subtitle":"Vybrat a nainstalovat n\u011Bkolik aplikac\u00ED najednou","AppPackPage.SelectedAppsTitle":"Vybran\u00E9 aplikace","AppPackPage.SelectedAppsLabel":"Vybran\u00E9 aplikace: {0}","AppPackPage.NoAppsSelected":"Nevybraly se \u017E\u00E1dn\u00E9 aplikace. Za\u010Dn\u011Bte v\u00FDb\u011Brem aplikac\u00ED vlevo.","AppPackPage.MaximumAppsWarning":"Maxim\u00E1ln\u00ED po\u010Det {0} aplikac\u00ED, kter\u00E9 se daj\u00ED st\u00E1hnout najednou","AppPackPage.InstallSingleButton":"Nainstalovat","AppPackPage.InstallMultipleButton":"Nainstalovat {0} aplikac(e/\u00ED)","AppPackPage.DownloadingButton":"Stahov\u00E1n\u00ED...","AppPackPage.DownloadingStatus":"Stahov\u00E1n\u00ED...","AppPackPage.DownloadingMessage":"Stahujeme spustiteln\u00FD soubor pro instalaci v\u00E1mi vybran\u00FDch aplikac\u00ED. Za\u010Dn\u011Bte t\u00EDm, \u017Ee ho spust\u00EDte.","AppPackPage.PostInstallMessage":"St\u00E1hli jsme spustiteln\u00FD soubor pro instalaci va\u0161ich aplikac\u00ED. Spus\u0165te jej ze slo\u017Eky Sta\u017Een\u00E9 soubory, abyste mohli za\u010D\u00EDt. ","AppPackPage.PostInstallMessage-Secondary":"N\u011Bkter\u00E9 aplikace se nainstaluj\u00ED na pozad\u00ED.","AppPackPage.RemoveAppAriaLabel":"Odebrat {0}","AppPackPage.ToggleShoppingCartAriaLabel":"n\u00E1kupn\u00ED voz\u00EDk","AppPackCollection.Productivity":"Produktivita","AppPackCollection.Creativity":"Kreativita","AppPackCollection.Social":"Soci\u00E1ln\u00ED s\u00EDt\u011B","AppPackCollection.AI":"AI","AppPackCollection.Entertainment":"Z\u00E1bava","AppPackCollection.ToolsUtilities":"N\u00E1stroje a pom\u016Fcky","AppPackCollection.Personalization":"P\u0159izp\u016Fsoben\u00ED","AppPackCollection.SelectAppAriaLabel":"Vyberte {0}","AppPackCollection.ViewDetailsAriaLabel":"Zobrazit podrobnosti o {0}","AppPackCollection.SignInRequired":"Pokud chcete z\u00EDskat tento produkt, p\u0159ihlaste se.","AppPackCollection.VerifyRequired":"K zakoupen\u00ED tohoto produktu je nutn\u00E9 ov\u011B\u0159it sv\u016Fj v\u011Bk.","AppPackCollection.DismissAlertAriaLabel":"Zav\u0159\u00EDt","ProductGallery.LoadErrorTitle":"Aplikaci se nepovedlo na\u010D\u00EDst","ProductGallery.LoadErrorMessage":"Tuto aplikaci se n\u00E1m nepovedlo na\u010D\u00EDst. Zkuste aplikaci vyhledat a zkusit to znovu.","ProductEvent.AvailableNow":"K\u00A0dispozici nyn\u00ED","ProductEvent.AvailableOn":"K dispozici na: {0}","ProductEvent.Ended":"Ukon\u010Deno","ProductEvent.InOneTimeUnit":"Za 1 {0}","ProductEvent.InTime":"Za {0} {1}","ProductEvent.OneTimeUnitLeft":"Zb\u00FDv\u00E1 1 {0}","ProductEvent.TimeLeft":"Zb\u00FDvaj\u00EDc\u00ED doba: {0} {1}","ProductEvent.CardAction":"Dal\u0161\u00ED informace o: {0}","Collections.curated.best-photo-and-video-editing-apps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace pro \u00FApravu fotografi\u00ED a vide\u00ED pro Windows \u2013 nejlep\u0161\u00ED n\u00E1stroje pro \u00FApravy z Microsoft Store pro retu\u0161ov\u00E1n\u00ED obr\u00E1zk\u016F, vytv\u00E1\u0159en\u00ED vide\u00ED a vylep\u0161ov\u00E1n\u00ED m\u00E9di\u00ED.","Collections.curated.racing-games.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED z\u00E1vodn\u00ED hry pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejlep\u0161\u00ED simul\u00E1tory aut, motocykl\u016F a \u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED z kolekce z\u00E1vodn\u00EDch her v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.new-and-notable-pc-games.Page.Description":"Nov\u00E9 a zaj\u00EDmav\u00E9 hry pro PC \u2013 prozkoumejte nejnov\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED a nejzaj\u00EDmav\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED hry pro Windows vydan\u00E9 v Microsoft Store nap\u0159\u00ED\u010D \u017E\u00E1nry.","Collections.curated.windows-themes.Page.Description":"Motivy Windows a styly plochy \u2014 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si kolekce tapet, vizu\u00E1ln\u00EDch motiv\u016F a p\u0159izp\u016Fsoben\u00ED plochy z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.best-entertainment-apps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED z\u00E1bavn\u00ED aplikace pro Windows \u2013 streamujte hudbu, videa, podcasty a medi\u00E1ln\u00ED n\u00E1stroje z nejlep\u0161\u00EDch aplikac\u00ED Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.best-productivity-apps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED kancel\u00E1\u0159sk\u00E9 aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejlep\u0161\u00ED n\u00E1stroje pro spr\u00E1vu \u00FAkol\u016F, po\u0159izov\u00E1n\u00ED pozn\u00E1mek, pr\u00E1ci v kancel\u00E1\u0159i a optimalizaci pracovn\u00EDch postup\u016F z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.music-streaming-apps.Page.Description":"Hudebn\u00ED aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 streamujte, vytv\u00E1\u0159ejte a u\u017Eijte si hudbu s vyu\u017Eit\u00EDm \u0161pi\u010Dkov\u00FDch zvukov\u00FDch aplikac\u00ED, p\u0159ehr\u00E1va\u010D\u016F hudby a streamovac\u00EDch slu\u017Eeb z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.social-and-news-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace soci\u00E1ln\u00EDch m\u00E9di\u00ED pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 spojte se s p\u0159\u00E1teli, sd\u00EDlejte obsah a udr\u017Eujte si p\u0159ehled d\u00EDky nejlep\u0161\u00EDm aplikac\u00EDm soci\u00E1ln\u00EDch s\u00EDt\u00ED v Microsoft Storu.","Collections.curated.kids-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry pro d\u011Bti ve Windows \u2013 objevte z\u00E1bavn\u00E9, bezpe\u010Dn\u00E9 a vzd\u011Bl\u00E1vac\u00ED hry z Microsoft Store ide\u00E1ln\u00ED pro d\u011Bti v\u0161ech v\u011Bkov\u00FDch kategori\u00ED.","Collections.curated.most-popular-utility-apps.Page.Description":"N\u00E1stroje pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nepostradateln\u00E9 n\u00E1stroje pro optimalizaci syst\u00E9mu, spr\u00E1vu soubor\u016F a ka\u017Edodenn\u00ED v\u00FDpo\u010Detn\u00ED \u00FAlohy z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.weather-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace p\u0159edpov\u011Bdi po\u010Das\u00ED pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 sledujte p\u0159edpov\u011Bdi, podm\u00EDnky a upozorn\u011Bn\u00ED s p\u0159esn\u00FDmi aplikacemi p\u0159edpov\u011Bdi po\u010Das\u00ED z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.reading-apps.Page.Description":"\u010Ctec\u00ED aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 u\u017Eijte si elektronick\u00E9 knihy, \u010Dl\u00E1nky a digit\u00E1ln\u00ED obsah s aplikacemi pro \u010Dten\u00ED a knihovny z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.remote-learning-apps.Page.Description":"Vzd\u011Bl\u00E1vac\u00ED aplikace pro PC \u2013 prozkoumejte vzd\u011Bl\u00E1vac\u00ED aplikace v Microsoft Store pro vzd\u00E1len\u00E9 u\u010Den\u00ED, rozvoj dovednost\u00ED a online kurzy.","Collections.curated.essential-apps.Page.Description":"Z\u00E1kladn\u00ED aplikace pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si z Microsoft Storu aplikace pro zv\u00FD\u0161en\u00ED produktivity, komunikaci, zabezpe\u010Den\u00ED a ka\u017Edodenn\u00ED \u010Dinnosti na po\u010D\u00EDta\u010Di.","Collections.curated.best-creativity-apps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace pro kreativitu pro Windows \u2013 navrhujte, kreslete, upravujte a tvo\u0159te pomoc\u00ED \u0161pi\u010Dkov\u00FDch kreativn\u00EDch n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro um\u011Blce a tv\u016Frce z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.getting-started-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro za\u010D\u00E1te\u010Dn\u00EDky pro nov\u00E9 po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De s Windows \u2013 nastavte si za\u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED pomoc\u00ED z\u00E1kladn\u00EDch aplikac\u00ED z Microsoft Store pro za\u010D\u00E1te\u010Dn\u00EDky a nov\u00E9 u\u017Eivatele.","Collections.curated.personalization-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro p\u0159izp\u016Fsoben\u00ED pro Windows \u2013 p\u0159izp\u016Fsobte si plochu, tapety, ikony a motivy pomoc\u00ED \u0161pi\u010Dkov\u00FDch n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro p\u0159izp\u016Fsoben\u00ED z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.security-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace zabezpe\u010Den\u00ED pro Windows \u2013 chra\u0148te sv\u016Fj po\u010D\u00EDta\u010D pomoc\u00ED nejlep\u0161\u00EDho antiviru, VPN, spr\u00E1vce hesel a n\u00E1stroje na ochranu soukrom\u00ED z Microsoft Storu.","Collections.curated.gaming-apps.Page.Description":"Hern\u00ED aplikace pro Windows \u2013 vylep\u0161ete sv\u00E9 hern\u00ED z\u00E1\u017Eitky na PC pomoc\u00ED streamov\u00E1n\u00ED, hlasov\u00E9ho chatu, n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro zv\u00FD\u0161en\u00ED v\u00FDkonu a dopl\u0148kov\u00FDch aplikac\u00ED z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.music-creation-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro tvorbu hudby pro Windows \u2013 skl\u00E1dejte, nahr\u00E1vejte, mixujte a produkujte hudbu pomoc\u00ED \u0161pi\u010Dkov\u00FDch n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro audio produkci a DAW z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.top-developer-apps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace pro v\u00FDvoj\u00E1\u0159e pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si vysoce kvalitn\u00ED aplikace od p\u0159edn\u00EDch v\u00FDvoj\u00E1\u0159\u016F a d\u016Fv\u011Bryhodn\u00FDch vydavatel\u016F v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.digital-pen-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro digit\u00E1ln\u00ED pera pro Windows \u2013 kreslete, pi\u0161te a vkl\u00E1dejte pozn\u00E1mky pomoc\u00ED aplikac\u00ED z Microsoft Store optimalizovan\u00FDch pro stylusy pro Surface Pen a dotykov\u00E1 za\u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED.","Collections.curated.kids-educational-apps.Page.Description":"Vzd\u011Bl\u00E1vac\u00ED aplikace pro d\u011Bti ve Windows \u2013 z\u00E1bavn\u00E9 v\u00FDukov\u00E9 hry, aplikace pro \u010Dten\u00ED, matematiku a p\u0159\u00EDrodn\u00ED v\u011Bdy pro d\u011Bti z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.home-improvement-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro vylep\u0161en\u00ED domova pro Windows \u2013 pl\u00E1nujte renovace, interi\u00E9rov\u00FD design, kutilsk\u00E9 projekty a v\u00FDzdobu domova pomoc\u00ED n\u00E1stroj\u016F Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.movie-making-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro tvorbu film\u016F pro Windows \u2013 vytv\u00E1\u0159ejte, upravujte a produkujte videa pomoc\u00ED \u0161pi\u010Dkov\u00FDch n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro tvorbu film\u016F, animac\u00ED a \u00FApravu videa z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.professional-apps.Page.Description":"Profesion\u00E1ln\u00ED aplikace pro Windows \u2013 pr\u016Fmyslov\u00E9 n\u00E1stroje Microsoft Store pro in\u017Een\u00FDrstv\u00ED, architekturu, anal\u00FDzu dat a pracovn\u00ED postupy v podnik\u00E1n\u00ED.","Collections.curated.best-video-streaming-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace pro streamov\u00E1n\u00ED videa pro Windows \u2013 sledujte filmy, televizn\u00ED po\u0159ady a \u017Eiv\u00E9 vys\u00EDl\u00E1n\u00ED pomoc\u00ED nejlep\u0161\u00EDch streamovac\u00EDch slu\u017Eeb a p\u0159ehr\u00E1va\u010D\u016F m\u00E9di\u00ED z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.top-free-apps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED bezplatn\u00E9 aplikace pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejobl\u00EDben\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED bezplatn\u00E9 aplikace z Microsoft Store pro produktivitu, z\u00E1bavu a ka\u017Edodenn\u00ED pou\u017Eit\u00ED.","Collections.curated.xbox-play-anywhere-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry Xbox Play Anywhere \u2013 kupte si je jednou a hrajte na Xboxu i Windows PC s podporou k\u0159\u00ED\u017Eov\u00E9ho ukl\u00E1d\u00E1n\u00ED z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.battery-efficient-apps.Page.Description":"Aplikace s n\u00EDzkou spot\u0159ebou baterie pro Windows \u2013 lehk\u00E9 aplikace z Microsoft Store optimalizovan\u00E9 pro dlouhou v\u00FDdr\u017E baterie v notebooc\u00EDch a tabletech.","Collections.curated.core-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry pro PC \u2013 objevte nejl\u00E9pe hodnocen\u00E9 hry pro Windows v \u017E\u00E1nrech ak\u010Dn\u00EDch, RPG, strategick\u00FDch a dobrodru\u017En\u00FDch her v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.classic-pc-games.Page.Description":"Klasick\u00E9 po\u010D\u00EDta\u010Dov\u00E9 hry \u2013 vra\u0165te se k nad\u010Dasov\u00FDm obl\u00EDben\u00FDm a legend\u00E1rn\u00EDm titul\u016Fm pro Windows, kter\u00E9 jsou k dispozici v obchod\u011B Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.casual-pc-games.Page.Description":"Neform\u00E1ln\u00ED PC hry \u2013 hrajte z\u00E1bavn\u00E9, snadno nau\u010Diteln\u00E9 hry pro Windows, kter\u00E9 jsou ide\u00E1ln\u00ED pro rychl\u00E9 hran\u00ED, z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.world-building-pc-games.Page.Description":"PC hry pro budov\u00E1n\u00ED sv\u011Bt\u016F \u2013 vytv\u00E1\u0159ejte, prozkoum\u00E1vejte a spravujte sv\u00E9 vlastn\u00ED sv\u011Bty v sandboxov\u00FDch, simula\u010Dn\u00EDch a stavebn\u00EDch hr\u00E1ch v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.puzzle-pc-games.Page.Description":"Logick\u00E9 hry pro PC \u2013 procvi\u010Dte si mozek s hlavolamy, logick\u00FDmi h\u00E1dankami a slovn\u00EDmi hrami z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.indie-pc-games.Page.Description":"Nez\u00E1visl\u00E9 PC hry \u2013 objevte jedine\u010Dn\u00E9, kreativn\u00ED a ocen\u011Bn\u00E9 nez\u00E1visl\u00E9 hry od talentovan\u00FDch v\u00FDvoj\u00E1\u0159\u016F v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.hidden-object-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry pro PC s hled\u00E1n\u00EDm skryt\u00FDch p\u0159edm\u011Bt\u016F \u2013 najd\u011Bte stopy, vy\u0159e\u0161te z\u00E1hady a prozkoumejte sc\u00E9ny v nejlep\u0161\u00EDch dobrodru\u017Estv\u00EDch s hled\u00E1n\u00EDm skryt\u00FDch p\u0159edm\u011Bt\u016F v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.gameloft-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry Gameloft pro PC \u2013 hrajte obl\u00EDben\u00E9 ak\u010Dn\u00ED, z\u00E1vodn\u00ED a dobrodru\u017En\u00E9 tituly od Gameloftu, kter\u00E9 jsou k dispozici v Microsoft Store pro Windows.","Collections.curated.microsoft-casual-pc-games.Page.Description":"Neform\u00E1ln\u00ED PC hry od Microsoftu \u2013 u\u017Eijte si Solitaire, Mahjong, Minesweeper a dal\u0161\u00ED bezplatn\u00E9 neform\u00E1ln\u00ED hry od Microsoftu v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.casino-pc-games.Page.Description":"Kasino PC hry \u2014 hrajte zdarma automaty, poker, blackjack a ruletu na Windows z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.xbox-game-studios-pc-games.Page.Description":"PC hry Xbox Game Studios \u2013 zahrajte si Halo, Forza, Age of Empires a dal\u0161\u00ED tituly od Xboxu v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.action-and-arcade-pc-games.Page.Description":"Ak\u010Dn\u00ED a ark\u00E1dov\u00E9 PC hry \u2013 rychl\u00E9 st\u0159\u00EDle\u010Dky, plo\u0161inovky a ark\u00E1dov\u00E9 klasiky pro Windows v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.cooking-games.Page.Description":"Kucha\u0159sk\u00E9 hry pro Windows \u2013 u\u017Eijte si z\u00E1bavu s restaurac\u00ED, pe\u010Den\u00EDm a kuchy\u0148sk\u00FDmi simul\u00E1tory z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.battle-pc-games.Page.Description":"Bojov\u00E9 PC hry \u2013 zapojte se do epick\u00FDch souboj\u016F v multiplayerov\u00FDch st\u0159\u00EDle\u010Dk\u00E1ch, battle royale a taktick\u00FDch v\u00E1le\u010Dn\u00FDch hr\u00E1ch v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.halo-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry Halo pro PC \u2013 zahrajte si legend\u00E1rn\u00ED sci-fi st\u0159\u00EDle\u010Dku na Windows s kampan\u011Bmi, multiplayerem a dal\u0161\u00EDmi funkcemi z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.space-pc-games.Page.Description":"Vesm\u00EDrn\u00E9 PC hry \u2013 prozkoumejte galaxie, pilotujte vesm\u00EDrn\u00E9 lod\u011B a dob\u00FDvejte vesm\u00EDr ve sci-fi hr\u00E1ch pro Windows v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.disney-pc-games.Page.Description":"PC hry Disney \u2013 za\u017Eijte kouzeln\u00E1 dobrodru\u017Estv\u00ED se sv\u00FDmi obl\u00EDben\u00FDmi postavami Disney, Pixar, Marvel a Star Wars v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.warhammer-pc-games.Page.Description":"PC hry Warhammer \u2013 bojujte ve ponur\u00E9m vesm\u00EDru se strategick\u00FDmi, ak\u010Dn\u00EDmi a RPG tituly Warhammer v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.king-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry King pro PC \u2013 zahrajte si Candy Crush, Farm Heroes a dal\u0161\u00ED n\u00E1vykov\u00E9 hry typu \u201Espoj 3\u201C a logick\u00E9 hry od King v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.big-fish-games-pc-games.Page.Description":"Big Fish Games pro PC \u2014 hrajte hry s hled\u00E1n\u00EDm skryt\u00FDch p\u0159edm\u011Bt\u016F, logick\u00E9 hry a p\u0159\u00EDle\u017Eitostn\u00E9 adventury od Big Fish v Microsoft Store pro Windows.","Collections.curated.clever-apps-universe.Page.Description":"Hry Clever Apps Universe \u2013 hrajte poutav\u00E9 logick\u00E9, simula\u010Dn\u00ED a dobrodru\u017En\u00E9 hry od Clever Apps v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.g5-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry G5 pro PC \u2013 hrajte hry s hled\u00E1n\u00EDm skryt\u00FDch p\u0159edm\u011Bt\u016F, kombinov\u00E1n\u00EDm t\u0159\u00ED a dobrodru\u017En\u00E9 hry od G5 Entertainment v Microsoft Store pro Windows.","Collections.curated.tilting-point-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry pro PC od Tilting Point \u2013 objevte bezplatn\u00E9 strategick\u00E9, simula\u010Dn\u00ED a dobrodru\u017En\u00E9 hry od Tilting Point v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.game-insight-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry Game Insight pro PC \u2013 hrajte hry od Game Insight zam\u011B\u0159en\u00E9 na budov\u00E1n\u00ED m\u011Bst, simulace a strategii v Microsoft Store pro Windows.","Collections.curated.playrix-pc-games.Page.Description":"Hry Playrix pro PC \u2013 zahrajte si Gardenscapes, Homescapes, Township a dal\u0161\u00ED logick\u00E9 hry typu \u201Espoj 3\u201C od Playrix v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.miracle-games-pc-games.Page.Description":"Miracle Games pro PC \u2014 hrajte RPG, strategick\u00E9 a ak\u010Dn\u00ED hry od Miracle Games v Microsoft Store pro Windows.","Collections.curated.weekly-pc-games-deals.Page.Description":"T\u00FDdenn\u00ED nab\u00EDdky PC her \u2013 u\u0161et\u0159ete d\u00EDky t\u00FDdenn\u00EDm slev\u00E1m na obl\u00EDben\u00E9 hry pro Windows z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.instant-games.Page.Description":"Okam\u017Eit\u00E9 hry \u2013 hrajte zdarma okam\u017Eit\u00E9 hry v prohl\u00ED\u017Ee\u010Di bez nutnosti stahov\u00E1n\u00ED, p\u0159\u00EDmo z Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.more-instant-games.Page.Description":"Dal\u0161\u00ED okam\u017Eit\u00E9 hry \u2013 objevte dal\u0161\u00ED bezplatn\u00E9 hry pro prohl\u00ED\u017Ee\u010De, kter\u00E9 m\u016F\u017Eete hr\u00E1t okam\u017Eit\u011B bez stahov\u00E1n\u00ED v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.tencent-pc-games.Page.Description":"PC hry Tencent \u2014 hrajte obl\u00EDben\u00E9 hry Tencent pro mobiln\u00ED za\u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED i PC, kter\u00E9 jsou k dispozici v obchod\u011B Microsoft Store pro Windows.","Collections.curated.in-game-deals.Page.Description":"Nab\u00EDdky ve h\u0159e \u2013 u\u0161et\u0159ete na DLC, sez\u00F3nn\u00EDch pasech, virtu\u00E1ln\u00ED m\u011Bn\u011B a obsahu ve h\u0159e pro sv\u00E9 obl\u00EDben\u00E9 hry pro Windows v Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.live-in-game-events.Page.Description":"\u017Div\u00E9 ud\u00E1losti ve hr\u00E1ch \u2013 objevte \u010Dasov\u011B omezen\u00E9 ud\u00E1losti, sez\u00F3nn\u00ED obsah a speci\u00E1ln\u00ED v\u00FDzvy, kter\u00E9 pr\u00E1v\u011B prob\u00EDhaj\u00ED ve hr\u00E1ch v Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopFree.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED bezplatn\u00E9 aplikace pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace z Microsoft Storu, v\u010Detn\u011B n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro produktivitu, u\u017Eite\u010Dn\u00FDch n\u00E1stroj\u016F a z\u00E1bavy.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED bezplatn\u00E9 hry pro PC a Windows \u2013 zahrajte si nejobl\u00EDben\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED hry z Microsoft Storu z \u017E\u00E1nr\u016F ak\u010Dn\u00EDch, logick\u00FDch a strategick\u00FDch her.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopPaid.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED placen\u00E9 aplikace pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace z Microsoft Storu, v\u010Detn\u011B n\u00E1stroj\u016F pro produktivitu, u\u017Eite\u010Dn\u00FDch n\u00E1stroj\u016F a z\u00E1bavy.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED placen\u00E9 hry pro PC a Windows \u2013 zahrajte si nejobl\u00EDben\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED hry z Microsoft Storu z \u017E\u00E1nr\u016F ak\u010Dn\u00EDch, logick\u00FDch a strategick\u00FDch her.","Collections.Curated.Bestphotoandvideoeditingapps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED aplikace pro \u00FApravu fotografi\u00ED a vide\u00ED pro Windows \u2013 nejlep\u0161\u00ED n\u00E1stroje pro \u00FApravy z Microsoft Store pro retu\u0161ov\u00E1n\u00ED obr\u00E1zk\u016F, vytv\u00E1\u0159en\u00ED vide\u00ED a vylep\u0161ov\u00E1n\u00ED m\u00E9di\u00ED.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopTrending.Page.Description":"Popul\u00E1rn\u00ED aplikace pro Windows \u2013 poznejte, co je pr\u00E1v\u011B te\u010F v Microsoft Storu nej\u017E\u00E1dan\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED: aplikace pro produktivitu, kreativitu a z\u00E1bavu.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Page.Description":"Popul\u00E1rn\u00ED hry pro PC a Windows \u2013 prohl\u00E9dn\u011Bte si nejobl\u00EDben\u011Bj\u0161\u00ED hry v Microsoft Storu, tituly nap\u0159\u00ED\u010D \u017E\u00E1nry a platformami.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Games.Primary.RacingGames._RacingGames.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED z\u00E1vodn\u00ED hry pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejlep\u0161\u00ED simul\u00E1tory aut, motocykl\u016F a \u0159\u00EDzen\u00ED z