je pro Windows \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejl\u00E9pe hodnocen\u00E9 leti\u0161tn\u00ED n\u00E1stroje, n\u00E1stroje pro v\u00FDvoj aplikac\u00ED a n\u00E1stroje pro \u0159idi\u010De kamion\u016F v Microsoft Storu.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopTrending.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Popul\u00E1rn\u00ED aplikace n\u00E1stroj\u016F a utilit pro Windows \u2013 prohl\u00E9dn\u011Bte si aktu\u00E1ln\u011B popul\u00E1rn\u00ED a rostouc\u00ED aplikace pro leti\u0161tn\u00ED slu\u017Eby, n\u00E1stroje pro v\u00FDvoj aplikac\u00ED a n\u00E1stroje pro \u0159idi\u010De kamion\u016F v Microsoft Storu.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.BestEntertainmentApps._BestEntertainmentApps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED z\u00E1bavn\u00ED aplikace pro Windows \u2013 streamujte hudbu, videa, podcasty a medi\u00E1ln\u00ED n\u00E1stroje z nejlep\u0161\u00EDch aplikac\u00ED Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.Bestproductivityapps._Bestproductivityapps.Page.Description":"Nejlep\u0161\u00ED kancel\u00E1\u0159sk\u00E9 aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nejlep\u0161\u00ED n\u00E1stroje pro spr\u00E1vu \u00FAkol\u016F, po\u0159izov\u00E1n\u00ED pozn\u00E1mek, pr\u00E1ci v kancel\u00E1\u0159i a optimalizaci pracovn\u00EDch postup\u016F z Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.ExploreAWorldOfMusic._ExploreAWorldOfMusic.Page.Description":"Hudebn\u00ED aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 streamujte, vytv\u00E1\u0159ejte a u\u017Eijte si hudbu s vyu\u017Eit\u00EDm \u0161pi\u010Dkov\u00FDch zvukov\u00FDch aplikac\u00ED, p\u0159ehr\u00E1va\u010D\u016F hudby a streamovac\u00EDch slu\u017Eeb z Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.ConnectAndStayInformed._ConnectAndStayInformed.Page.Description":"Aplikace soci\u00E1ln\u00EDch m\u00E9di\u00ED pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 spojte se s p\u0159\u00E1teli, sd\u00EDlejte obsah a udr\u017Eujte si p\u0159ehled d\u00EDky nejlep\u0161\u00EDm aplikac\u00EDm soci\u00E1ln\u00EDch s\u00EDt\u00ED v Microsoft Storu.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Games.Primary.PCGamesForKids._PCGamesForKids.Page.Description":"Hry pro d\u011Bti ve Windows \u2013 objevte z\u00E1bavn\u00E9, bezpe\u010Dn\u00E9 a vzd\u011Bl\u00E1vac\u00ED hry z Microsoft Store ide\u00E1ln\u00ED pro d\u011Bti v\u0161ech v\u011Bkov\u00FDch kategori\u00ED.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.MostPopularUtilityApps._MostPopularUtilityApps.Page.Description":"N\u00E1stroje pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 st\u00E1hn\u011Bte si nepostradateln\u00E9 n\u00E1stroje pro optimalizaci syst\u00E9mu, spr\u00E1vu soubor\u016F a ka\u017Edodenn\u00ED v\u00FDpo\u010Detn\u00ED \u00FAlohy z Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.WeatherApps._WeatherApps.Page.Description":"Aplikace p\u0159edpov\u011Bdi po\u010Das\u00ED pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 sledujte p\u0159edpov\u011Bdi, podm\u00EDnky a upozorn\u011Bn\u00ED s p\u0159esn\u00FDmi aplikacemi p\u0159edpov\u011Bdi po\u010Das\u00ED z Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.ReadingRoom._ReadingRoom.Page.Description":"\u010Ctec\u00ED aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 u\u017Eijte si elektronick\u00E9 knihy, \u010Dl\u00E1nky a digit\u00E1ln\u00ED obsah s aplikacemi pro \u010Dten\u00ED a knihovny z Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.AppsForLearningRemotely._AppsForLearningRemotely.Page.Description":"V\u00FDukov\u00E9 aplikace pro osobn\u00ED po\u010D\u00EDta\u010De \u2013 objevte vzd\u011Bl\u00E1vac\u00ED aplikace pro vzd\u00E1len\u00E9 u\u010Den\u00ED, rozvoj dovednost\u00ED a online kurzy z Microsoft Store.","Collection.Filter.AllProducts":"V\u0161echny produkty","Collection.Filter.AllCategories":"V\u0161echny kategorie","Collection.Filter.AllGenres